## 4. Geo-Hierarchy Network Topology (5 Tiers)

| Tier | Role | Scale |
|------|------|-------|
| Tier 5 (Edge) | Monolith Scout/Vanguard; general AI inference | 10M+ nodes |
| Tier 4 (Metro) | Aggregate proofs from Tier 5, batching | Metro-level |
| Tier 3 (National) | Traffic and data sovereignty | Country-level |
| Tier 2 (Regional) | Large model training (LLM) | Super nodes |
| Tier 1 (Global Root) | Space/Foundation nodes; global state root | Foundation |

